# Kawaii Sushi Stickers

Product details

Free shipping on orders $35+!

A variety of stickers in your choice of 5, 10, 15, 25, or 50 pack.

Made in the USA

🌍 All stickers are made from safe, non-toxic, phthalate, and chlorine-free
PEVA Vinyl (not PVC), making them safe for Kids, Pets, Water Bottles and
Crafting.

Check out my shop for more fandom stickers!

These stickers are:

-Durable and waterproof.

-Glossy

-Die-Cut

-Handmade

-UV resistant

They are created on quality vinyl to ensure longevity.

Great for water bottles, laptops, notebooks, or wherever you want to stick
them. They also make great gifts!

Stickers are between 2.5 - 3 inches each and are chosen randomly for each
order.

New customers receive a 10% discount code towards their next purchase!

Visit my website: stormsstickers.com for more stickers and exclusive offers!
